---
title: Creamy Dill Chicken with Lemony Carrot and Zucchini Ribbon Salad
description: This simple and quick weeknight dinner is light on carbs and calories but not on satisfaction! Juicy, golden seared chicken breasts are draped in a luscious dill sauce. A gorgeous salad of carrot and zucchini ribbons in a simple zesty vinaigrette perfectly finishes off the plate!

